{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"787927eead","title":"换彭雪枫联","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cee54bdae9","index":0,"year":1945,"month":2,"day":7,"articleId":"787927eead"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji19","name":"毛泽东全集第19卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji19.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji19":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c164dca316","type":"paragraph","text":"换彭雪枫联","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"787927eead"},{"id":"4b74211a4c","type":"paragraph","text":"（1945年2月7日）二十年限难事业，即将彻底完成，总看功绩辉煌，英名水垂，一世忠页，是共产党人好榜样千万里破碎河山，正待从头收拾，料血花飞溅，为国活胜满腔悲情，为中华民族悍英雄。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"787927eead"},{"id":"13d89f7d6d","type":"paragraph","text":"为民族，为群众，二十年奋斗出生入死，功垂祖国打日本，打汉坪，千百万同胞自由平等，泽被长准。[1]1944年9月11日，新四军第四师师长兼淮北军区司令员彭需模走河南夏色与日伪军作战中牡。1945年2月7日，延安各界举行追停彭雪权大会。本文一是毛泽东和朱德、刘少奇、彭德怀、陈教等联名送的找联。毛泽东还写了词。本文二是毛泽东代中共中央写的提联。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"787927eead"}],"page":{"id":"d6e08c1f17","publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"787927eead","start":300,"end":300}}}},"__N_SSG":true}